name: modifications
description: Modified amino acids and sites. Format: <Modifications>:<Position>;[...]

name: is_decoy
description: True if the ident is a decoy, False if ident is target

name: is_immutable
description: True if no suitable decoy could be generated for ident

name: exp_mz
description: Experimental m/z ratio, remapped by pyiohat using MS run metainfo

name: exp_mass
description: Experimental mass ratio, recalculated by pyiohat using MS run metainfo

name: ucalc_mz
description: Ursgal calculated m/z ratio, recalculated by pyiohat using ucalc_mass

name: ucalc_mass
description: Ursgal calculated C12 mass using the chemical formula as computed by chemical_composition

name: search_engine
description: Name and version of the utilized search engine
